"{\"uid\": \"skynews.com.au-australia-news-sport-aussie-football-fans-left-devastated-outraged-as-the-matildas-are-knocked-out-of-2024-paris-olympic-games-in-loss-to-usa-news-story-03d2a99b2bb06138e867128dc84afe6f\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Aussie football fans have been rocked by mixed emotions after the Matildas' gold medal dreams were dashed following a devastating loss to the United States.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 156, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 142, \"end\": 155, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999633590792624, \"rank\": 3.664220376298606e-05, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aussie football fans have been devastated and outraged after the Matildas suffered a crushing loss in its match up with the United States of America in the 2024 Paris Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 158, \"to\": 339, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 223, \"end\": 231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.512608389183983e-22, \"text\": \"Matildas\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Australian women's team only needed a draw to make it out of the group stage and secure a spot in the knockout round, but the final 2-1 result on Thursday morning (AEST) dashed their hopes of progressing.\", \"from\": 341, \"to\": 549, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 341, \"end\": 355, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.5763510505438042e-21, \"text\": \"The Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Australian\"}, {\"begin\": 509, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"AEST\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_in_Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following the loss, the Matildas needed Canada to either lose or draw in its match with Colombia to keep gold dreams alive but a 1-0 victory for the Canadians killed the Aussies' Olympics run.\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.512608389183983e-22, \"text\": \"Matildas\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 591, \"end\": 597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996471161, \"rank\": 3.465171421218157e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 639, \"end\": 647, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998108996985, \"rank\": 1.8910032878812156e-07, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A win for the Matildas in the USA match looked unlikely,\\u00a0with the side on the back foot against the opposition's fierce attack.\", \"from\": 745, \"to\": 872, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 775, \"end\": 778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999621207519614, \"rank\": 3.7880680507781104e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Leading 2-0 at 90 minutes, the Yanks seemed to have it in the bag until defender-turned-striker Alanna Kennedy slotted one in the back of the neck.\", \"from\": 874, \"to\": 1021, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 970, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alanna_Kennedy\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alanna Kennedy\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alanna_Kennedy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alanna_Kennedy\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A follow-up goal would unfortunately allude the new striker just minutes later when a header opportunity was not secured.\", \"from\": 1023, \"to\": 1144, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Matildas' X account shared a heartfelt message with its fans following its Paris departure that was overwhelmingly responded with messages of support.\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1300, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999877218, \"rank\": 1.2325553598594928e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While this four-year journey has ended, another one is just around the corner.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We ask that you stay with us, the Matildas family, as our story continues to unfold,\\\" it wrote.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1477, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Devastated fans shared their heartbreak in response to the post with many saying how proud they were of the team.\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1592, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Thank You, Australia \\u00f0\\u0178\\u00ab\\u00b6\\u00f0\\u0178'\\u0161\\u00f0\\u0178'\\u203aThank you for being with us and lifting us throughout every part of our journey over the past four years.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1732, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1605, \"end\": 1614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998854800717, \"rank\": 1.1163179813219384e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the late nights, the early wake-up calls, the joys and disappointments, and most importantly, for your unwavering support\\u00e2\\u20ac\\\"win, lose, or draw.\\u00e2\\u20ac\\u00a6pic.twitter.com/4dWaGNST0o  \\\"If any Australian girls need a big hug or some arms to cry into, to be consoled after this I am here,\\\" one fan wrote.\", \"from\": 1733, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"score\": 0.732637893747549, \"rank\": 0.36484600155952246, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_men's_national_rugby_league_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another shared: \\\"Disappointed but proud.\\\"\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2072, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Others, however, lashed out at the team's management, particularly its coach Tony Gustavsson who is rumoured to finish up in his position after the Paris Games.\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2151, \"end\": 2166, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Tony Gustavsson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tony_Gustavsson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a fail unfortunately.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Poor coaching & tactics.\", \"from\": 2264, \"to\": 2288, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Likely a few retirements in coming weeks to allow the next gen to progress,\\\" wrote one.\", \"from\": 2289, \"to\": 2376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another said: \\\"#TonyOut.\\\"\", \"from\": 2378, \"to\": 2403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One quipped: \\\"Let this be a lesson.\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2440, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Never again a foreign coach!\\\"\", \"from\": 2441, \"to\": 2470, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The game itself was not without controversy as a questionable decision from referee Francois Letexier rocked many fans who were left with seeing red.\", \"from\": 2472, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Just two minutes before half time the Americans put their first goal in the back of the net, but an impassioned request from Gustavsson, that saw him earn a yellow card, halted a final decision from the referee.\", \"from\": 2623, \"to\": 2834, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2748, \"end\": 2758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonas_Gustavsson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gustavsson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q11774891\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonas_Gustavsson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jonas_Gustavsson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"US forward Trinity Rodman scored off a corner but Australia's goalkeeper had her line of sight disrupted by an offside player, spurring the Aussies to contest the goal.\", \"from\": 2836, \"to\": 3004, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2836, \"end\": 2838, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9892870849782645, \"rank\": 0.010776365898368626, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2861, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Trinity Rodman\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Trinity_Rodman\"}, {\"begin\": 2886, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999998854800717, \"rank\": 1.1163179813219384e-07, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a technological mishap that contributed to a 10-minute delay on a final decision, Letexier gave America the goal.\", \"from\": 3006, \"to\": 3125, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One enraged fan lashed out at the controversial call, while others claimed the Aussies had no hope regardless.\", \"from\": 3127, \"to\": 3237, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The girls were robbed,\\\" one player posted.\", \"from\": 3239, \"to\": 3282, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A user responded to the claim: \\\"Did you watch the game?\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3339, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They hardly had any control of the field or the ball.\", \"from\": 3340, \"to\": 3393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's remarkable that they still scored, more remarkable that they kept it a low scoring game.\\\"\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Another replied: \\\"They have been poor all tournament.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3543, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hardly robbed\\\"  The quarter finals follow the end of the group stage with the USA facing off against Japan, Canada versing Germany, Spain heading toe-to-toe with Colombia and host-nation France battling Brazil.\", \"from\": 3544, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3622, \"end\": 3625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999621207519614, \"rank\": 3.7880680507781104e-05, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3645, \"end\": 3650, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7055204246836474, \"rank\": 0.4173934091774758, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan_women's_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3652, \"end\": 3658, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 0.9999999996471161, \"rank\": 3.465171421218157e-10, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.o